headline: Tractor Supply Celebrates Sponsorship of the U.S. Department of Agriculture’s Great American Farmers Market
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., August 01, 2025--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, today announced its participation as a title sponsor of the U.S. Department of Agriculture’s (USDA) 2025 Great American Farmers Market, which celebrates the nation’s farmers, ranchers and producers in anticipation of the United States’ 250th anniversary in 2026. The market will take place daily beginning Sunday, August 3, through Friday, August 8, from 4 to 8 p.m.
